3. IMPLEMENTATION SUMMARY
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Model:                 TopologyNode (ServiceNode, IngressNode, KafkaTopicNode, DatabaseNode, ConfigMapNode), TopologyEdge (EdgeType), ContainerPort, ResourceLimits, EnvVar, IngressRule
  KubernetesManifestParser:  Fabric8 Serialization.unmarshal; Deployment→ServiceNode (image, replicas, ports, resources, envVars), Service→ServiceNode, Ingress (networking.v1)→IngressNode, ConfigMap→ConfigMapNode
  MicronautConfigParser:     application.yml → HTTP_CALL, KAFKA_* edges, datasource url→DATABASE_CONNECT, optional Redis
  IstioManifestParser:       VirtualService, DestinationRule, Gateway → SERVICE_DEPENDENCY, INGRESS_ROUTE edges and metadata
  TopologyEnrichmentService: snapshotDir/k8s (nodes), config/<service>/application.yml + istio (edges); node/edge→config-artifacts docs; TopologyGraph→MinIO evidence/topology/{snapshotId}.json; returns TopologyResult(nodeCount, edgeCount)
  Parsers use:               io.fabric8.kubernetes.api.model.apps.Deployment, io.fabric8.kubernetes.api.model.networking.v1.Ingress

